data.description: This BEAUTIFUL remodeled all brick house is screaming your name! Located in the Timberland Plantation just minutes away Cordele! This house features all the bells and whistles you can imagine starting with Granite countertops, in ground pool, custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances and a 9 zone sprinkler irrigation system! Pool has recently  been resurfaced along with 2 HVAC units! One of the units is just 4 months old and the other is 4 years old. Located in the living room is a gas fireplace that can be used as a wood burning fireplace to keep your friends, family and guests cozy! Just off to the living room you have 4 bedrooms, including 3 spare bedrooms, one could make a great office/study and Master. The spare bedrooms have a jack and Jill bathroom. The master bathroom checks all the boxes including tiled shower, tub, double vanities and a huge walk in closet! There's more! The outside includes a covered deck and an open patio that overlooks the pool!Call for a private showing!
